   Use a dictionary to count the number of occurrences of each letter 
   in some text and display the counts in alphabetical order. Do not
   display any letter that does not occur in the text.
   This is the letter counting lab from chapter 12.
   ~~~~
   text = '''Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers.
   A peck of pickled peppers Peter Piper picked.
   If Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers
   Where's the peck of pickled peppers Peter Piper picked?'''
   
   #Add code here to count the letters and print the results.